Content: ————————————————————————NLNLNL                                  __**About Drop**__NLNLNL————————————————————————NLNLTeam Drop Is A Clan That Is A Semi Competitive Clan.We Take Players From All Around The World.We Also Take People On Any Platform.NLNL```How To Tryout```NLNLFirst You Must Join The Server.Then When You See Tryout Application Copy And Paste What It Says In The Channel.Then You Paste It To The Leader And After You Do After (A) Put Your Answer.NLNL```How You May Tryout```NLNLYou May Tryout By Doing Pubs Or Doing 1v1s With The Leader.NLNL```Requirements```NL•Fast Builds.NL•Fast 90s.NL•You Know How To Edit.NL•You Know How To Aim.(No Need To Lazar People)NLNL```Goals```NLNLOur Goal Is To Hit 150 Members By Then End Of This Month So We Can Start Doing Scrims And Snipes_So Just Joining Will Help Hit Our Goal.
